trailingComments.value:
*
 * Sets the spawn point for a player.
 *
 * @example
 * const spawnpoint = new Spawnpoint(
 *   new Player('Mike'),
 *   new Coordinate(10, 20, 30) // optional
 * );
 * @see
 * http://minecraft.gamepedia.com/Commands#spawnpoint

arguments.value: player should be an instance of Player
arguments.raw: 'player should be an instance of Player'

arguments.value: coordinate should be an instance of Coordinate
arguments.raw: 'coordinate should be an instance of Coordinate'
